Enum Class Food

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Food>
model.food.Food
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Food>, Constable
public enum Food extends Enum<Food>
The Food enumeration. Lists all the foods that exists. Uses the category emun for the kind of food, the NutritionalValue for the nutritional value and the Freshnesslevel for the freshness level of the food. Also has a some methods besides that, getters and setters.
